        '3 bedrooms plus study': how bedroom count and configuration affect Brisbane property value
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Bedroom count is the first filter buyers apply on portals, before price, before suburb, before anything else. Getting the description right matters more than most sellers realise.
      </p>
